    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Ana holds a safe angle and lands Biotic Rifle shots to heal allies or chip enemy health, saving Sleep Dart to stop a dive or Biotic Grenade to shut down enemy sustain before a big fight.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>Her kit is entirely projectile-based with travel time, so heroes who close distance quickly can pressure her before she gets a chance to use her utility at all.</p>"
